---
title: Buenos Días Black Bean Bowls with Chunky Guacamole and a Fried Egg Topper
description: Rice and beans are the pinnacle of comfort food. Are they nourishing? Absolutely. Have you ever gotten really jazzed about the combo? ...We thought so. Well, our chef-innovators have officially broken them out of their comfort-zone (in the very best way)! We’re talking a mixture of cheesy rice and black beans topped with chunky guacamole, tangy lime crema, and—last but not least—perfectly fried eggs. It’s a dish that’s as easy to make as it is deliciously satisfying. Say buenos días to your new fave meal!
